data.name: Darkly-42Network
data.description: Introductory project to computer security in the specific field of the web, this project will make you dissect a vulnerable website. In doing so, you will develop your own way of thinking about security in a web application and become aware of the problems associated with simple development errors, both from a programming point of view and from a design point of view.
